ontent\/uploads\/2019\/10\/html-export-trong-Ladipage-768x358.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/html-export-trong-Ladipage.png 1274w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>Xu\u1ea5t trang web \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 download v\u1ec1 m\u00e1y t\u00ednh v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ea1ng html<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ed5i t\u00ean file th\u00e0nh <code>index.html<\/code> \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1edbi b\u01b0\u1edbc k\u1ebf ti\u1ebfp.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn b\u01b0\u1edbc k\u1ebf ti\u1ebfp, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u01b0u \u00fd c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1ec1 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf m\u00e0 Ladipage mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed nh\u01b0 sau:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Form t\u1ea1o b\u1edfi Ladipage s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 g\u1eedi th\u00f4ng tin qua email m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 API hay c\u00e1c d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 email marketing li\u00ean k\u1ebft. B\u1ea1n n\u00ean d\u00f9ng Form t\u1eeb b\u00ean th\u1ee9 3 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u00fang v\u00e0o trang (d\u00f9ng HTML Element khi t\u1ea1o trang) nh\u01b0 <a href=\"\/out\/formget\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">Pabbly Form<\/a> hay c\u00e1c d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9c l\u1eadp. Kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean d\u00f9ng Form c\u1ee7a Ladipage.<\/li><li>B\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i \u0111i\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin SEO v\u00e0 m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Google Analytics \u0111\u1ec3 khi xu\u1ea5t file html s\u1ebd t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng k\u00e8m theo.<\/li><li>T\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed s\u1ebd t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng remark trang v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t widget nh\u1ecf b\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi, nh\u01b0ng khi b\u1ea1n xu\u1ea5t file html th\u00ec s\u1ebd t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf remark n\u00e0y. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 y\u00ean t\u00e2m.<\/li><li>T\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed s\u1ebd b\u1ecb h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf kho m\u1eabu thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf s\u1eb5n, trong khi t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n tr\u1ea3 ph\u00ed s\u1ebd truy c\u1eadp \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 kho thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf m\u1eabu. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, v\u1eabn l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 \u0111\u1ee7 cho b\u1ea1n l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn.<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/bang-gia-cua-ladipage.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"659\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/bang-gia-cua-ladipage-1024x659.png\" alt=\"Bang Gia Cua Ladipage\" class=\"wp-image-22348\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/bang-gia-cua-ladipage-1024x659.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/bang-gia-cua-ladipage-218x140.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/bang-gia-cua-ladipage-300x193.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/bang-gia-cua-ladipage-700x450.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/bang-gia-cua-ladipage-768x494.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/bang-gia-cua-ladipage.png 1282w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>B\u1ea3ng gi\u00e1 v\u00e0 so s\u00e1nh t\u00ednh n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed Ladipage<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>\u1ede b\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y, n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111am m\u00ea v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n d\u00f9ng Ladipage tr\u1ea3 ph\u00ed theo th\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i h\u01a1n th\u00ec b\u1ea1n h\u00e3y ng\u01b0ng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u00e0 mua g\u00f3i tr\u1ea3 ph\u00ed. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n n\u1ebfu th\u1ea5y \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"highlight\">C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt: Hi\u1ec7n t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed Ladipage \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n t\u00ednh n\u0103ng xu\u1ea5t file HTML n\u1eefa, th\u1eadt \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng Brizy Cloud thay th\u1ebf.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 quen v\u1edbi <a href=\"\/out\/brizypro\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Brizy Page Builder (opens in a new tab)\">Brizy Page Builder<\/a> th\u00ec Brizy Cloud l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn kh\u00f4ng t\u1ec7 cho b\u1ea1n. D\u00f9 file xu\u1ea5t ra k\u00e8m theo folder asset nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec v\u00ec c\u00e1ch l\u00e0m c\u0169ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 Ladipage.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"tip\"><span class=\"title\">Ch\u00fa \u00dd<\/span>\n<p>T\u00ednh n\u0103ng t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u1ed9 server c\u1ee7a Brizy Cloud s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng d\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Sau khi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 trong tay m\u1ed9t file <code>index.html<\/code> th\u00ec vi\u1ec7c k\u1ebf ti\u1ebfp s\u1ebd l\u00e0 host file \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trang web &#8220;live&#8221;.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"pk-heading-numbered\">Hosting mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed cho trang web t\u0129nh: Github Page<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 host trang web t\u0129nh tr\u00ean r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u host nh\u01b0 Amazon S3, Google Cloud, <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"pCloud (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"\/out\/pcloud\" target=\"_blank\">pCloud<\/a>, Google Drive,&#8230;nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch host ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o h\u01a1n \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 <a href=\"https:\/\/pages.github.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Github Page (opens in a new tab)\">Github Page<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>D\u00e0nh cho nh\u1eefng b\u1ea1n ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft th\u00ec <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Github (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https:\/\/github.com\/\" target=\"_blank\">Github<\/a> l\u00e0 c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 ph\u1ea3i bi\u1ebft c\u1ee7a m\u1ecdi l\u1eadp tr\u00ecnh vi\u00ean. Github gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t USB online cao c\u1ea5p dung l\u01b0\u1ee3ng <strong>1GB<\/strong> v\u00e0 Github Page l\u00e0 t\u00ednh n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 bi\u1ebfn USB \u0111\u00f3 &#8220;live&#8221;.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Microsoft \u0111\u00e3 mua l\u1ea1i Github v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 7.5 t\u1ef7 USD (n\u0103m 2018) v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed kh\u00f4ng gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng private repository cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi bi\u1ebfn Github v\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1t tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh si\u00eau ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn tr\u00ean to\u00e0n c\u1ea7u. Github th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 nghi\u00eam t\u00fac c\u1ee7a Microsoft.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>L\u00fd do b\u1ea1n n\u00ean d\u00f9ng Github Page l\u00e0:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed.<\/li><li>Kh\u00f4ng gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n Public Repository (1 Repo l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t website).<\/li><li>T\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 cao.<\/li><li>Mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed ch\u1ee9ng ch\u1ec9 SSL.<\/li><li>C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng t\u00ean mi\u1ec1n ri\u00eang (custom domain).<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u1ec3 host file <code>index.html<\/code> b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u00ean m\u00e1y t\u00ednh, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n Github (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https:\/\/github.com\/join\" target=\"_blank\">t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n Github<\/a> v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o xong m\u1ed9t Public Repository.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n l\u00e0m theo h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn b\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o nhanh m\u1ed9t Public Repository.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/tao-mot-public-repository-moi.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"471\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/tao-mot-public-repository-moi-1024x471.png\" alt=\"Tao Mot Public Repository Moi\" class=\"wp-image-22359\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/tao-mot-public-repository-moi-1024x471.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/tao-mot-public-repository-moi-218x100.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/tao-mot-public-repository-moi-300x138.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/tao-mot-public-repository-moi-700x322.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/tao-mot-public-repository-moi-768x353.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/tao-mot-public-repository-moi.png 1919w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>B\u01b0\u1edbc 1: Sau khi c\u00f3 t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n Github, b\u1ea1n b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1o m\u1ed9t Public Repository m\u1edbi<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/tao-public-repository-voi-ten-ngan-gon.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"673\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/tao-public-repository-voi-ten-ngan-gon-1024x673.png\" alt=\"Tao Public Repository Voi Ten Ngan Gon\" class=\"wp-image-22360\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/tao-public-repository-voi-ten-ngan-gon-1024x673.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/tao-public-repository-voi-ten-ngan-gon-218x143.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/tao-public-repository-voi-ten-ngan-gon-300x197.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/tao-public-repository-voi-ten-ngan-gon-700x460.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/tao-public-repository-voi-ten-ngan-gon-768x505.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/tao-public-repository-voi-ten-ngan-gon.png 1235w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>B\u01b0\u1edbc 2: \u0110\u1eb7t t\u00ean cho Repo, ch\u1ecdn Public v\u00e0 b\u1ea5m n\u00fat kh\u1edfi t\u1ea1o<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/tai-len-file-index-da-tao.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"646\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/tai-len-file-index-da-tao-1024x646.png\" alt=\"Tai Len File Index Da Tao\" class=\"wp-image-22361\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/tai-len-file-index-da-tao-1024x646.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/tai-len-file-index-da-tao-218x138.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/tai-len-file-index-da-tao-300x189.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/tai-len-file-index-da-tao-700x442.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/tai-len-file-index-da-tao-768x485.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/tai-len-file-index-da-tao.png 1236w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>B\u01b0\u1edbc 3: T\u1ea3i file index.html \u1edf tr\u00ean m\u00e1y t\u00ednh b\u1ea1n (\u0111\u00e3 download \u1edf t\u1eeb Ladipage)<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Sau khi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 upload <code>index.html<\/code> l\u00ean Github, ch\u1edd kho\u1ea3n 10 ph\u00fat b\u1ea1n truy c\u1eadp v\u00e0o&nbsp;<code>usergithubname.github.io<\/code>&nbsp;tr\u00ean tr\u00ecnh duy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eed xem trang web c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 &#8220;live&#8221; ch\u01b0a.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>N\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5y trang web c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 xin ch\u00fac m\u1eebng b\u1ea1n c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o nh\u1eefng trang kh\u00e1c b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1o trang tr\u00ean Ladipage, xu\u1ea5t file v\u00e0 upload l\u00ean. Trang ch\u1ee7 cho website b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t t\u00ean l\u00e0 <code>index.html<\/code>. C\u00e1c trang kh\u00e1c b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd \u0111\u1eb7t t\u00ean nh\u01b0 <code>lien-he.html<\/code> v\u00e0 <code>policy.html<\/code>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ch\u00fa \u00fd l\u00e0 t\u00ean c\u1ee7a file c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 trang URL. V\u00ed du:&nbsp;<code>usergithubname.github.com\/lien-he.html<\/code>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"pk-heading-numbered\">T\u1ea1o t\u00ean mi\u1ec1n ri\u00eang cho trang web mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed b\u1eb1ng Cloudflare v\u00e0 Github Page<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Github Page c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>1 GB l\u01b0u tr\u1eef<\/li><li>100 GB bandwidth<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Nh\u01b0 b\u1ea1n th\u1ea5y, b\u0103ng th\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 <strong>100GB<\/strong>. V\u00ec v\u1eady, ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m b\u0103ng th\u00f4ng l\u00e0 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n t\u1ea1o trang b\u1eb1ng Ladipage th\u00ec t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u1ea3nh b\u1ea1n t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 upload trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u1ea1o trang s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u01b0u \u1edf Ladipage v\u00e0 \u1ea3nh c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c CDN c\u1ee7a Ladipage n\u1eefa.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>C\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m b\u0103ng th\u00f4ng, v\u00ec v\u1eady t\u00f4i m\u1edbi khuy\u1ebfn kh\u00edch b\u1ea1n d\u00f9ng Ladipage thay v\u00ec c\u00e1c d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 kh\u00e1c.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1eabn tr\u00ean tinh th\u1ea7n ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m c\u00e0ng nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t. \u0110\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u traffic th\u00ec sao.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>T\u1ea1i sao l\u1ea1i c\u1ea7n d\u00f9ng <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Cloudflare (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https:\/\/www.cloudflare.com\/\" target=\"_blank\">Cloudflare<\/a> b\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 cho Github Page?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t combo v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u1eefu d\u1ee5ng b\u1ed5 sung nh\u1eefng thi\u1ebfu s\u00f3t c\u1ee7a Github Page. Cloudflare gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n 4 vi\u1ec7c ch\u00ednh sau:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd DNS \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 t\u00ean mi\u1ec1n ri\u00eang cho Github Page.<\/li><li>C\u1ea5p ch\u1ee9ng ch\u1ec9 SSL mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng.<\/li><li>Cache.<\/li><li>T\u1ed1i \u01b0u t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9.<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<h3>C\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh t\u00ean mi\u1ec1n ri\u00eang cho trang web<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 quan tr\u1ecdng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n v\u00e0o th\u1ebb <strong>setting<\/strong> trong <strong>Public Repository<\/strong> &gt;&gt; Ch\u1ecdn th\u1ebb <strong>Settings<\/strong> nh\u01b0 h\u00ecnh<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/Vao-the-setting-cua-Github-Page.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"273\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/Vao-the-setting-cua-Github-Page-1024x273.png\" alt=\"Vao The Setting Cua Github Page\" class=\"wp-image-22323\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/Vao-the-setting-cua-Github-Page-1024x273.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/Vao-the-setting-cua-Github-Page-218x58.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/Vao-the-setting-cua-Github-Page-300x80.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/Vao-the-setting-cua-Github-Page-700x187.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/Vao-the-setting-cua-Github-Page-768x205.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/Vao-the-setting-cua-Github-Page.png 1800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>B\u01b0\u1edbc 1: V\u00e0o th\u1ebb Setting c\u1ee7a Public Reposity m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/Github-Pages-setting.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"544\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/Github-Pages-setting-1024x544.png\" alt=\"Github Pages Setting\" class=\"wp-image-22322\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/Github-Pages-setting-1024x544.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/Github-Pages-setting-218x116.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/Github-Pages-setting-300x159.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/Github-Pages-setting-700x372.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/Github-Pages-setting-768x408.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/Github-Pages-setting.png 1409w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>B\u01b0\u1edbc 2: Ch\u1ecdn Master Branch. <br>(B\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 upload file <code>index.html th\u00ec<\/code> m\u1edbi ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c <strong>master branch<\/strong>)<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/custom-domain-cua-Github-Page.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"696\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/custom-domain-cua-Github-Page-1024x696.png\" alt=\"Custom Domain Cua Github Page\" class=\"wp-image-22326\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/custom-domain-cua-Github-Page-1024x696.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/custom-domain-cua-Github-Page-218x148.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/custom-domain-cua-Github-Page-300x204.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/custom-domain-cua-Github-Page-700x476.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/custom-domain-cua-Github-Page-768x522.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/custom-domain-cua-Github-Page.png 1257w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>B\u01b0\u1edbc 3: \u0110\u00e1nh t\u00ean mi\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n v\u00e0o \u00f4 Custom Domain v\u00e0 copy Github User URL c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ebft, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n \u0110\u1ea2M B\u1ea2O b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n <strong>Name Server t\u00ean mi\u1ec1n<\/strong> c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n sang Cloudflare \u0111\u1ec3 Cloudflare qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd DNS cho b\u1ea1n. (<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"\/client\/knowledge-base\/module\/quan-ly-dns\/\" target=\"_blank\">Xem h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn tham kh\u1ea3o c\u00e1ch chuy\u1ec3n Nameserver c\u1ee7a Namesilo sang Cloudflare n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft<\/a>).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n v\u00e0o Tab DNS c\u1ee7a Cloudflare v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o m\u1ed9t <code>CNAME record<\/code> v\u1edbi <code>@<\/code> v\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb l\u00e0 <code>usergithub.github.io<\/code> (URL m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 copy \u1edf tr\u00ean).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/cach-cau-hinh-custom-domain-trong-Cloudflare-voi-github-pages.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"430\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/cach-cau-hinh-custom-domain-trong-Cloudflare-voi-github-pages-1024x430.png\" alt=\"Cach Cau Hinh Custom Domain Trong Cloudflare Voi Github Pages\" class=\"wp-image-22331\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/cach-cau-hinh-custom-domain-trong-Cloudflare-voi-github-pages-1024x430.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/cach-cau-hinh-custom-domain-trong-Cloudflare-voi-github-pages-218x92.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/cach-cau-hinh-custom-domain-trong-Cloudflare-voi-github-pages-300x126.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/cach-cau-hinh-custom-domain-trong-Cloudflare-voi-github-pages-700x294.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/cach-cau-hinh-custom-domain-trong-Cloudflare-voi-github-pages-768x323.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/cach-cau-hinh-custom-domain-trong-Cloudflare-voi-github-pages.png 1574w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>B\u01b0\u1edbc 4: T\u1ea1o CNAME record \u1edf Cloudflare v\u00e0 Save<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n nh\u1edb b\u1eadt \u0111\u00e1m m\u00e2y m\u00e0u cam l\u00ean.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"tip\"><span class=\"title\">Ch\u00fa \u00dd<\/span>\n<p>C\u00e1ch t\u1ea1o CNAME record n\u00e0y \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng khi b\u1ea1n d\u00f9ng t\u00ean mi\u1ec1n ch\u00ednh. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n d\u00f9ng t\u00ean mi\u1ec1n ph\u1ee5 nh\u01b0 <code>pages.domain.com<\/code> th\u00ec \u1edf \u00f4 <b>Name<\/b> b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd \u0111i\u1ec1n l\u00e0 <code>pages<\/code> thay cho <code>@<\/code>.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<h3>Thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp Cache Everything tr\u00ean Cloudflare<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 WordPress website th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i b\u1eadt Cache Everything cho static site.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>M\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ecbnh Cloudflare s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng cache html n\u00ean b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp cache html b\u1eb1ng Page Rule c\u1ee7a Cloudflare.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, s\u1eb5n ti\u1ec7n b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng s\u1ebd th\u00eam 2 Cloudflare rule quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 HTTPS always v\u00e0 Redirect 301 cho t\u00ean mi\u1ec1n ph\u1ee5 <code>www<\/code>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/thiet-lap-Cloudflare-page-rule.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"607\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/thiet-lap-cloudflare-page-rule-1024x607.png\" alt=\"Thiet Lap Cloudflare Page Rule\" class=\"wp-image-22461\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/thiet-lap-cloudflare-page-rule-1024x607.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/thiet-lap-cloudflare-page-rule-218x129.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/thiet-lap-cloudflare-page-rule-300x178.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/thiet-lap-cloudflare-page-rule-700x415.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/thiet-lap-cloudflare-page-rule-768x455.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/thiet-lap-cloudflare-page-rule.png 1339w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>T\u1ea1o Page Rule quan tr\u1ecdng \u201cCache Everything\u201d v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n ti\u1ec7n t\u1ea1o lu\u00f4n 2 page rules ph\u1ee5 h\u1eefu \u00edch<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"tip\"><span class=\"title\">Ch\u00fa \u00dd<\/span>\n<p>Cloudflare ch\u1ec9 mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed 3 rule cho t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. Nh\u01b0 b\u1ea1n th\u1ea5y tr\u00ean h\u00ecnh, Cloudflare b\u1eaft b\u1ea1n mua th\u00eam Page Rule khi \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n 3 Page Rule.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<h3>C\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t Full SSL Cloudflare<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>\u1ede th\u1ebb SSL\/TLS c\u1ee7a Cloudflare, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n chuy\u1ec3n sang Full. Ch\u1edd m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat \u0111\u1ec3 Cloudflare t\u1ea1o ch\u1ee9ng ch\u1ec9 cho site c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/SSL-cho-github-page.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"620\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/SSL-cho-github-page-1024x620.png\" alt=\"Ssl Cho Github Page\" class=\"wp-image-22341\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/SSL-cho-github-page-1024x620.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/SSL-cho-github-page-218x132.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/SSL-cho-github-page-300x182.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/SSL-cho-github-page-700x424.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/SSL-cho-github-page-768x465.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/SSL-cho-github-page.png 1190w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>B\u1eadt &#8220;Full&#8221; \u0111\u1ec3 trang web b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 HTTPS<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n nh\u1edb l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eadt \u0111\u00e1m m\u00e2y m\u00e0u cam cho t\u00ean mi\u1ec1n ri\u00eang record \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o \u1edf th\u1ebb DNS b\u01b0\u1edbc 1 \u1edf tr\u00ean.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Xong, b\u00e2y gi\u1edd b\u1ea1n th\u1eed \u0111\u00e1nh t\u00ean mi\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n v\u00e0o tr\u00ecnh duy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m tra xem trang web c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 live ch\u01b0a nh\u00e9.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"pk-heading-numbered\">T\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng SEO trang web Github Page c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>V\u1ec1 SEO th\u00ec b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o th\u00eam m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i file n\u1eefa bao g\u1ed3m:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Trang 404 (404.html)<\/li><li>robot.txt<\/li><li>sitemap.xml<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n t\u1ea1o m\u1ed9t trang 404 t\u00f9y ch\u1ec9nh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch t\u1ea1o trang nh\u01b0 tr\u00ean v\u00e0 upload l\u00ean Github Page.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>V\u1edbi <code>robot.txt<\/code> th\u00ec b\u1ea1n t\u1ea1o m\u1ed9t file robot ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng bao g\u1ed3m sitemap nh\u01b0 sau:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>User-agent: *\nSitemap: http:\/\/www.example.com\/sitemap.xml<\/code><\/pre>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o sitemap b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.xml-sitemaps.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https:\/\/www.xml-sitemaps.com\/<\/a>&nbsp;mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed. B\u1ea1n n\u00ean t\u1ea1o sitemap sau khi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh xong t\u00ean mi\u1ec1n ri\u00eang. Khi \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd v\u00e0o v\u00e0 nh\u1eadp t\u00ean mi\u1ec1n ri\u00eang c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o sitemap v\u00e0 upload l\u00ean Github.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"204\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/XML-Sitemap-1024x204.png\" alt=\"Xml Sitemap\" class=\"wp-image-22367\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/XML-Sitemap-1024x204.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/XML-Sitemap-218x43.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/XML-Sitemap-300x60.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/XML-Sitemap-700x139.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/XML-Sitemap-768x153.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/XML-Sitemap.png 1210w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption>Nh\u1eadp t\u00ean mi\u1ec1n b\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n v\u00e0o v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 s\u1ebd t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea1o sitemap cho b\u1ea1n (download v\u00e0 up l\u00ean Github)<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>M\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n b\u1ea1n upload trang m\u1edbi, b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i t\u1ea1o l\u1ea1i sitemap v\u00e0 upload sitemap m\u1edbi l\u00ean Github. Th\u1eadt ra, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea1o sitemap b\u1eb1ng Jellky nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u trang n\u00ean t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u00e1ch t\u1ea1o sitemap th\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng n\u00e0y s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 v\u1edbi b\u1ea1n h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n th\u00eam site v\u00e0o trong Google Search Console nh\u01b0 th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec3 Google ch\u1ec9 m\u1ee5c trang web b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2>L\u1eddi k\u1ebft&#8230;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m m\u1ed9t trang m\u1eabu cho b\u1ea1n tham kh\u1ea3o: <a rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https:\/\/github.cuongthach.com\" target=\"_blank\">https:\/\/github.cuongthach.com<\/a> v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ch\u00e8n Facebook Live Chat v\u00e0 Opt-in Popup.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>C\u00e1ch t\u1ea1o n\u00e0y \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t khi b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n t\u1ea1o m\u1ed9t website c\u00f4ng ty ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9 tin c\u1eady v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p th\u00f4ng tin li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c nh\u1edd hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec7n tr\u00ean internet. \u00c1p d\u1ee5ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t cho m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh B2B.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>M\u1ed9t tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00e1c h\u1eefu d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u1ea1o nhanh m\u1ed9t trang CV online ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o (Porfolio Page), gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ed9ng l\u1edbn trong m\u1eaft nh\u00e0 tuy\u1ec3n d\u1ee5ng hay \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o trang b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng online \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n (n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m) s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m chi ph\u00ed t\u1ea1o website v\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea1y qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0o c\u00e1c m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 t\u1ea1o trang tuy\u1ec3n d\u1ee5ng, s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n, chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch khuy\u1ebfn m\u00e3i,&#8230;t\u00f9y v\u00e0o mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 b\u1ea1n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 vi\u1ebft blog \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y nh\u01b0ng m\u00ecnh ngh\u0129 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean v\u00ec WordPress \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1t cho blog v\u1edbi SEO t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. Khi b\u1ea1n vi\u1ebft blog b\u1eb1ng Github th\u00ec s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi nhi\u1ec1u k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a l\u1eadp tr\u00ecnh vi\u00ean, c\u00e1i m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd m\u1ea5t r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian h\u1ecdc d\u00f9ng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Trong khi WordPress l\u1ea1i qu\u00e1 thu\u1eadn ti\u1ec7n cho blog, b\u1ea1n n\u00ean d\u00f9ng WordPress \u0111\u1ec3 vi\u1ebft blog thay v\u00ec blog &#8220;t\u0129nh&#8221;.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n, h\u00e3y \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn b\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi, t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n s\u1eb5n l\u00f2ng gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n!<\/em><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>C\u00e1ch mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t trang web s